content.rendered:
The Carlos Stackable chair can be used in a wide range of areas; be it meeting rooms, waiting rooms, dining areas and many more.

The Carlos Chair has a soft upholstered seat and backrest, solid wood armrest pads made from beech and a solid chrome plated metal frame.

Stackable up to 4 high. Leather faced.

This item carries a 3 year guarantee

Available for delivery in 10 working days.
